119
00:06:16,642 --> 00:06:18,284
into every aspect of game design.

120
00:06:20,589 --> 00:06:23,231
These techniques are often considered to be dirty,

121
00:06:23,471 --> 00:06:25,653
because they force you into these compulsion loops,

122
00:06:25,713 --> 00:06:27,054
or trying to get you to spend money.

123
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:28,716
But they don't have to be that way.

124
00:06:29,256 --> 00:06:31,578
Used properly and generously, these techniques

125
00:06:31,638 --> 00:06:33,440
can actually be beneficial.

126
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:36,022
Our industry has grown, and we've changed,

127
00:06:36,042 --> 00:06:39,424
and we've gone beyond the point where just your gut feeling,

128
00:06:40,125 --> 00:06:42,447
that isn't enough to predict whether or not

129
00:06:42,487 --> 00:06:44,208
your game is going to be successful anymore.

130
00:06:45,305 --> 00:06:47,305
