131
00:06:47,846 --> 00:06:51,107
It's about making something that will impress, inspire,

132
00:06:51,487 --> 00:06:53,708
and really impact people's lives.

133
00:06:57,089 --> 00:06:59,150
And to me, this is the heart of level design.

134
