You create the part of the game that faces out to the player,

135
00:07:03,051 --> 00:07:04,892
the part that gives them that touch point

136
00:07:05,272 --> 00:07:08,633
to interact with whatever crazy ideas and concepts

137
00:07:08,673 --> 00:07:10,074
your team has come up with.

