stumbled in blindly and I thought that if I had enough information, if I could just get all

140
00:07:20,951 --> 00:07:25,333
these numbers and everything in front of me, I could make sense of them. But I actually

141
00:07:25,373 --> 00:07:32,477
ended up overwhelmed and it was all way, way more difficult than it appeared. So a little

142
00:07:32,497 --> 00:07:38,720
bit of audience participation. How many of you have ever heard of the company Trafodata?

